  "detailed_description": "<br>\"Warehouse Inc.\" is more than just a game — it's a test of skill, speed, and strategy. Do you have what it takes to conquer the world of logistics and become the ultimate warehouse employee?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/6c86a7bfeb8cd872ddf4b47bc46a2827.avif?t=1714505973\" width=800 height=100 /></span><br>One of your main responsibilities is to accept new shipment. Make sure to accept it in time!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/4daa46f8d2d9e6b8bc4bd4143980b275.poster.avif?t=1714505973\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/4daa46f8d2d9e6b8bc4bd4143980b275.webm?t=1714505973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/4daa46f8d2d9e6b8bc4bd4143980b275.mp4?t=1714505973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/fc67edac792a5bad8d6ee08eac9d3dac.avif?t=1714505973\" width=800 height=100 /></span><br>Keep track of each package by scanning shipping labels to find an exact order and destination it has to be delivered.<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/0d791081759de6d230ef99ca60d7ccc1.poster.avif?t=1714505973\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/0d791081759de6d230ef99ca60d7ccc1.webm?t=1714505973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/0d791081759de6d230ef99ca60d7ccc1.mp4?t=1714505973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/25127d4398ab15ac251bf81382ddef58.avif?t=1714505973\" width=800 height=100 /></span><br>Space is limited but you have a lot of orders. Everything needs to be delivered in time. Make sure to organize it!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/ed9536efa0b5330a4413c512ff776d61.poster.avif?t=1714505973\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/ed9536efa0b5330a4413c512ff776d61.webm?t=1714505973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/ed9536efa0b5330a4413c512ff776d61.mp4?t=1714505973\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/bab3734f4f821fdbd024416b4a55bf48.avif?t=1714505973\" width=800 height=100 /></span><br>Deliver, deliver, deliver! Make sure every package is delivered. Only the best employees can keep the job!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/a2ccc120153b22cbabc1da8d8b3d9c69.poster.avif?t=1714505973\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/a2ccc120153b22cbabc1da8d8b3d9c69.webm?t=1714505973\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2886930/extras/a2ccc120153b22